      "source_ref": "note:row705450#s3",
      "text": "Pt had no LOC at the scene and was MAE s."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row705450:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He was brought to ED     where he was scanned and an occipital head laceration w",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row705450#s4",
      "text": "He was brought to ED     where he was scanned and an occipital head laceration was stapled."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row705450:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Scans revealed negative Head CT, C-spine clear radiographically and    clinicall",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row705450#s5",
      "text": "Scans revealed negative Head CT, C-spine clear radiographically and    clinically,  yet torso scan showed T11 vertebral body fx, T9 and T10    spinus process fx s, the T10 fx extending inferiorly to the facets and    leading to an anterior sublaxation of the T10 vertebral body over the    T11 vertbral body, small fragments noted posterior to the T10 cord."
    },
